<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.6.8">
<l>kurakkiṉat tālē kuraikaṭal taṉṉai</l>
<l>nerukki yaṇaikaṭṭi nīṇī rilaṅkai</l>
<l>yarakka raviya vaṭukaṇai yālē</l>
<l>nerukkiya kaikaḷāl cappāṇi nēmiyaṅ kaiyaṉē cappāṇi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having beseiged the roaring ocean with a group of monkeys,</l>
<l>having built a bridge [across] the deep water,</l>
<l>[clap] cappāṇi with the hands that assailed the demons of Laṅkā</l>
<l rend="indent">with destructive arrows so that they perished!</l>
<l>You with the hands [that bear] the discus, [clap] cappāṇi!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
